created front end - npm create vite@latest
created server folder

server - bcrypt ,cloudinary, cors, express, mongoose, dotenv, jsonwebtoken, multer, paypal-rest-sdk


client: axios, react-router-dom


>server -  npm init -y: it will create package.json folder in server folder
    create server.js: then in package.json -> change to "main": "index.js",=> "main": "server.js",

    npm i --save-dev nodemon: create package.lock.json and some change in package.json

    update - "start": "server.js"
            "dev": "nodemon server.js"


    then: npm i bcrypt cloudinary cors express mongoose dotenv jsonwebtoken multer paypal-rest-sdk

>client:- 
    npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer

    npx tailwindcss init -p
    update: content: ["./src/**/*.{html,js}"],=> in tailwind.config file

    update :@tailwind base;
            @tailwind components;
            @tailwind utilities;  => in index.css

        shadcn => create jsconfig.json file =>   
                    update ""compilerOptions": {
                    "baseUrl": ".",
                    "paths": {
                    "@/*": ["./src/*"]
                    }
                }"
    replace: in vite.config.js => 
        "import path from "path"
        import react from "@vitejs/plugin-react"
        import { defineConfig } from "vite"

        export default defineConfig({
        plugins: [react()],
        resolve: {
            alias: {
            "@": path.resolve(__dirname, "./src"),
            },
        },
        })"

    install -> npx shadcn@latest init

    install => npx shadcn@latest add button

    run - npm run dev

    install - npm i axios react-router-dom
              npx shadcn@latest add tabs
              npx shadcn@latest add card
            npx shadcn@latest add input label select textarea card toast skeleton switch dropdown-menu checkbox






